text: Ochromima pallipes is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Olivier in 1795. It is known from French Guiana and Surinam.BioLib.cz - Ochromima pallipes. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. There are no catalogued subspecies ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1795
